milestones.description: Dayle Hadlee has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs, going past Harilal Shah's 2
Alvin Kallicharran has broken the record for most sixes (2) in ODIs for WI, going past Clive Lloyd's 1
Alvin Kallicharran has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Fredericks's record
Hastings has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for NZ, going past Howarth's 3
Keith Boyce has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for WI, going past Fredericks
Hastings has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (11) for NZ, going past Glenn Turner
Alvin Kallicharran has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 264 runs, going past Fredericks's 212
Glenn Turner and Geoff Howarth's 90-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 53 between John Morrison and Barry Hadlee
